name: K/DA Akali (shrouded form) Pop/stars
description:
Club Euphoria Collective presents...
ceejay x utsy - K/DA Akali (shrouded form) Pop/stars

"The main inspiration behind this K/DA Akali fan art is the fact that I became kinda obsessed with the bright neon colors from her shrouded form, I did my best to match the colors as close to the in-game version as possible"

"It was a fun collab…having to animate and put sound on this masterpiece. 
It just pops!"
-utsy
